SnapEngage,is,a,live,chat,solution,that,allows,a,business,support,team,to,interact,with,site,visitors,in,real,time,The,SnapEngage,API,allows,developers,to,interface,SnapEngage,with,third,party,applications,Using,the,API,SnapEngage,can,automatically,POST,events,to,an,external,URL,when,new,requests,are,received,either,offline,or,live,chat,This,transaction,provides,detailed,information,pertaining,to,the,request,and,allows,developers,to,recreate,the,request,in,the,destination,system,The,API,uses,HTTP,protocol,and,resposnes,are,formatted,in,XML